summary: Preset of my current wood elf character
descriptionHtml:
Sylence is one of my newest character. She is a Bosmer (Wood elf).

Background:

Sylence was born on a stormy night.. However, as the skies flashed with bright lightening, the night was silent. Other than the rain, there was no other sounds that accompanied the dangerous skies. So, her parents named her Sylence...

Anyway, in order for this to look right, you need a few things:

SKSE and Racemenu
SG Renewal
Eyes of Aber
KS Hairdos
UNP Body
SG Brows
Ethereal Elven Overhaul

I believe that is all. This is the first time I have uploaded a preset. Anyway, enjoy.
author: Fatal Syn
